The '''Private University of Science and Arts''' was a private university in [[Aleppo]], [[Syria]], established in 2003. It has two faculties:  [[Architecture]] and [[Fine Arts]]. The owner of the university Farid Jwala. The university were the first private university open up in Syria. The university were in the middle of Aleppo

